Titolo: No Straight Roads

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: No Straight Roads is an action-adventure video game developed by Malaysian independent studio Metronomik and published by Sold Out Ltd. The focus is on an indie rock duo who battle an EDM empire to free Vinyl City from their control with the power of rock. The game combat involves listening to the music, knowing when enemies attack and when to strike. It was released worldwide on August 25, 2020, for the PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch, and PC via the Epic Games Store after three years of development and several delays due to the COVID-19 pandemic.The updated version of the game, No Straight Roads: Encore Edition was announced after a year of the game release, and was released worldwide on October 21, 2021, on Steam.